headline: The New Year Is Almost Here and Disney Has an Exciting Present for Shareholders
summary: Tired Disney (NYSE: DIS) shareholders are finally getting a break from their disappointment.  Disney stock, which has been on the way down for a few years, perked up recently, and it's gained 16% over the past month.  Let's not get carried away with Disney's gain; at the time of this writing, Disney stock remains 42% off of its five-year highs.
